        "content": "<p>I would like to consider R[x_1,...,x_n] as an R[x_1]-module. I guess that what I need is an instance of  <code>Module (Polynomial R) (MvPolynomial (Fin (n + 1)) R)</code> but I'm stuck on how to define it. Could someone give a hint please?</p>",
